Jordan Sharifi, 17, was taken into custody on Friday by police in McKinney, Texas . 
  He allegedly confessed to giving a gun and ammunition to his friend Raymond Howell, Jr . 
  Howell was found dead in a ditch on Thursday from a self-inflicted gunshot wound . 
  Sharifi found his friend's body after he got a call from the boy's mother . 
  He says he stole a gun from a family he was staying with and gave it to Howell to protect him from bullies . 
  He said he found the gun beneath Howell's body and confessed to police that he had given the boy the gun . 
  Howell had reportedly asked for a transfer from McKinney Boyd High School because he was being bullied . 
 